  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">International Aid Transparency Initiative (IATI)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The International Aid Transparency Initiative aims to deliver a step shift in public availability and accessibility of information on aid flows and activities globally. It does this by bringing together donors partner countries CSOs and other users of aid 
information to agree a set of common standards applicable to all aid flows. Launched at the Accra High Level Forum on Aid Effectiveness the initiative now has 28 donor signatories and a growing number of endorsements from partner countries.</narrative>
  </description>
